    "description": {
      "value": "<em>As you become suffused with power, you become more and more like an elemental.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Elemental overflow class feature, kineticist level 15th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Whenever you have accepted at least 4 points of burn, the chance to ignore the effects of a critical hit or sneak attack increases by an additional 10%. This chance increases by an additional 5% for every 2 points of burn you accept after that. This chance can't exceed 100%. <br/><br/><b>Normal</b><br/>Whenever you have accepted at least 3 points of burn, your chance to ignore the effects of a critical hit or sneak attack equals 5% x your current number of points of burn.",
